room_title: Escape room "Hungover" by Br8kout Escape Rooms in Milwaukee
room_description: Fabulous Las Vegas. It was a great night wasn’t it?!?! Shame you can’t remember a thing. What happened? How did we all get here, and where are the car keys? We have to get it together. Security is showing up in one hour to kick us out because of all the trouble we caused last night. Does the slogan “What happens in Vegas stays in Vegas” apply to what we did last night?
